00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:18.959
officials currently vacillating

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:20.680
will recognize the shift in power.

00:01:21.599 --> 00:01:23.040
If Shi Yu reveals the seal,

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:24.799
Gao Ji will lose

00:01:24.799 --> 00:01:26.599
his legitimate authority
to deploy troops.

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:27.959
Gao Ji values

00:01:28.439 --> 00:01:29.400
his reputation most.

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:31.920
