00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:35.319
He might even

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:36.519
lose his composure.

00:01:37.319 --> 00:01:38.760
But Gao Ji already knows

00:01:39.159 --> 00:01:40.680
you won't willingly be his puppet.

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:41.920
Therefore,

00:01:42.319 --> 00:01:43.920
you must appear weak recently,

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.239
and let him think

00:01:45.519 --> 00:01:46.280
you know limits,

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:47.808
and will stay out of his way

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:48.992
under his control.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:50.359
That's right.

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:52.840
We'll lull Gao Ji into complacency,

00:01:53.319 --> 00:01:55.760
and also urgently locate
the imperial seal's hiding place.

